latestIgtvVideos.title: Here I present, glimpse of my , 18 months weightloss journey..
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I still remember tht vry frst day wen I rejoined gym , post delivery.. My trainer looked at me for few seconds and said BAHUT MEHNAT KARNI PADEGI APKO, The moment he said tht I had tears in my eyes 😭
Though it was a c- section, so I was not allowed to do weight training for long .. 
I started my workout routine with slow cardio and kept improving it gradually. 
Felt more motivated from the time I started seeing results.. 
➡️ when covid thing happened and everything was closed during pandemic including gyms , everyone started questioning about my workout routine, bt I took it as challenge and since thn m working out at home and m thankful to each one of u for appreciating my efforts 🙏🏻😇
Thankyu @anishaweightlossdiet for guiding me during initial months. 
And Thankyu @fitnessformula1 for being der in my fatloss journey.
